graph TD
    Client["Client SDK"] -->|POST /api/v1/*| API["FastAPI Gateway"]
    
    API -->|Enqueue train/save reqs| Queue["Async Request Queue"]
    
    subgraph GPU 0: PyTorch Trainer
        Queue -->|Drain & Batch| Clock["Clock Cycle Engine"]
        Clock --> Swap["set_active_adapter()"]
        Swap --> Train["Forward/Backward & Optim"]
        Swap --> Save["model.save_pretrained()"]
    end
    
    Save -->|Sync .safetensors| RAMDisk[("RAM Disk (/tmp/open-rl)")]
    
    API -->|Route inference reqs| IPC["HTTP / HTTPX IPC"]
    
    subgraph GPU 1: vLLM Inference
        IPC --> vLLM["vLLM Worker Subprocess"]
        RAMDisk -->|Load LoRARequest| vLLM
        vLLM --> Gen["Generate (PagedAttention)"]
    end
    
    Train -->|Write Future| Store["Futures Store"]
    Gen -->|Write Future| Store
    Save -->|Write Future| Store
    
    Client -->|Poll /retrieve_future| Store
